social_posts.post_text: You don’t want to go back to the basics. 🖤
My energy kinetic. I’m painting full pictures of my perspective. 💛

‘What is Most Truly Valuable is Often Underrated’
-
Vol.1: DiCaprio Bootle, Kansas City Chiefs

The Sun Beaming. 7 Notes, it’s GodGiven❤️.

1. My skillset is unmatched. My mind is dominant. I can say this with my chest, I am one of the best.

2. By the time you see it, I’ve done it already. Super Future. Like a Wizard.

3. Memento Mori! The level of happiness in your life depends on the quality of your thoughts.

4. Comparison is the ultimate thief of joy. Be You.

5. Mindset of an Elitist. Consistency is a lost art.

6. Don’t let life throw you wild cards. Be The Joker. I am dangerous but I am also in control.

7. The main thing is ALWAYS the main thing. In all walks of life. Unapologetically.

It’s love. Thank you God. 🔋
